1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,440
Hoy me he dado

2
00:00:00,440 --> 00:00:01,280
una vuelta

3
00:00:01,280 --> 00:00:02,720
por Mestalla en bici...

4
00:00:02,720 --> 00:00:04,000
y mirad lo que

5
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:04,840
me he encontrado.

6
00:00:04,840 --> 00:00:05,320
Una mesita

7
00:00:05,320 --> 00:00:05,680
de cafe

8
00:00:05,680 --> 00:00:06,360
de madera.

9
00:00:06,360 --> 00:00:07,000
Con un lijado

10
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:07,800
y un barniz

11
00:00:07,800 --> 00:00:08,880
queda perfecta.

12
00:00:08,880 --> 00:00:09,360
Ahi estaba,

13
00:00:09,360 --> 00:00:10,280
esperando.

14
00:00:10,280 --> 00:00:10,680
Tu vecino

15
00:00:10,680 --> 00:00:11,240
de dos calles

16
00:00:11,240 --> 00:00:12,040
mas alla

17
00:00:12,040 --> 00:00:12,800
puede que necesite

18
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:13,920
justo esto.

19
00:00:13,920 --> 00:00:14,880
Y no lo sabe.

20
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:15,800
Y sabeis que hago yo

21
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:16,320
cuando encuentro

22
00:00:16,320 --> 00:00:17,160
algo asi?

23
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:18,040
Lo subo a Givore.

24
00:00:18,040 --> 00:00:18,520
Foto,

25
00:00:18,520 --> 00:00:19,080
titulo,

26
00:00:19,080 --> 00:00:19,960
y listo.

27
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:20,520
Ahora alguien

28
00:00:20,520 --> 00:00:21,520
del barrio

29
00:00:21,520 --> 00:00:22,280
puede verla

30
00:00:22,280 --> 00:00:22,720
y darle

31
00:00:22,720 --> 00:00:23,840
otra oportunidad.

32
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:25,360
Antes de tirar algo...

33
00:00:25,360 --> 00:00:26,440
pensad si alguien

34
00:00:26,440 --> 00:00:27,440
lo puede aprovechar.

35
00:00:27,440 --> 00:00:27,960
Nos vemos

36
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:28,920
en el proximo paseo.

